import React from 'react';
import './assets/styles/global.css';
import { Actions } from './actions.js';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client';
import { Homepage }  from './homepage.js';
import { Error404 } from './404.js';
import { CustomPage } from './customPage.js';
import { Uploader } from './uploader.js'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom';
import { ChooseTheme } from './choose_theme.js';
import { Success } from './success.js';
import { Fail } from './fail.js'
import { Login } from './login.js'
import { CreateAccount } from './create_account.js';
import { FetchAndDeleteFiles } from './delete_file.js';

function App()
{
	return (
		<Router>
			<Routes>
				<Route path='/' element={ <Homepage /> }/>
				<Route path='/actions' element={ <Actions /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/custom_page' element={ <CustomPage /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/uploader' element={ <Uploader /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/choose_theme' element={ <ChooseTheme /> }/>
				<Route path='/success' element={ <Success /> }/>
				<Route path='/fail' element={ <Fail /> }/>
				<Route path='/login' element={ <Login />}/>
				<Route path='/createaccount' element= {<CreateAccount />} />
				<Route path='/action/delete_file' element= {<FetchAndDeleteFiles />} />
				<Route path='*' element={ <Error404 /> }/>
			</Routes>
		</Router>
	);
}

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'));
root.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <App />
  </React.StrictMode>
);

import React from 'react';
import './assets/styles/global.css';
import { Actions } from './actions.js';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client';
import { Homepage }  from './homepage.js';
import { Error404 } from './404.js';
import { CustomPage } from './customPage.js';
import { Uploader } from './uploader.js'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom';
import { ChooseTheme } from './choose_theme.js';
import { Success } from './success.js';
import { Fail } from './fail.js'
import { Login } from './login.js'
import { CreateAccount } from './create_account.js';
import { FetchAndDeleteFiles } from './delete_file.js';

function App()
{
	return (
		<Router>
			<Routes>
				<Route path='/' element={ <Homepage /> }/>
				<Route path='/actions' element={ <Actions /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/custom_page' element={ <CustomPage /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/uploader' element={ <Uploader /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/choose_theme' element={ <ChooseTheme /> }/>
				<Route path='/success' element={ <Success /> }/>
				<Route path='/fail' element={ <Fail /> }/>
				<Route path='/login' element={ <Login />}/>
				<Route path='/createaccount' element= {<CreateAccount />} />
				<Route path='/action/delete_file' element= {<FetchAndDeleteFiles />} />
				<Route path='*' element={ <Error404 /> }/>
			</Routes>
		</Router>
	);
}

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'));
root.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <App />
  </React.StrictMode>
);

import React from 'react';
import './assets/styles/global.css';
import { Actions } from './actions.js';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client';
import { Homepage }  from './homepage.js';
import { Error404 } from './404.js';
import { CustomPage } from './customPage.js';
import { Uploader } from './uploader.js'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom';
import { ChooseTheme } from './choose_theme.js';
import { Success } from './success.js';
import { Fail } from './fail.js'
import { Login } from './login.js'
import { CreateAccount } from './create_account.js';
import { FetchAndDeleteFiles } from './delete_file.js';

function App()
{
	return (
		<Router>
			<Routes>
				<Route path='/' element={ <Homepage /> }/>
				<Route path='/actions' element={ <Actions /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/custom_page' element={ <CustomPage /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/uploader' element={ <Uploader /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/choose_theme' element={ <ChooseTheme /> }/>
				<Route path='/success' element={ <Success /> }/>
				<Route path='/fail' element={ <Fail /> }/>
				<Route path='/login' element={ <Login />}/>
				<Route path='/createaccount' element= {<CreateAccount />} />
				<Route path='/action/delete_file' element= {<FetchAndDeleteFiles />} />
				<Route path='*' element={ <Error404 /> }/>
			</Routes>
		</Router>
	);
}

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'));
root.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <App />
  </React.StrictMode>
);

import React from 'react';
import './assets/styles/global.css';
import { Actions } from './actions.js';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client';
import { Homepage }  from './homepage.js';
import { Error404 } from './404.js';
import { CustomPage } from './customPage.js';
import { Uploader } from './uploader.js'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom';
import { ChooseTheme } from './choose_theme.js';
import { Success } from './success.js';
import { Fail } from './fail.js'
import { Login } from './login.js'
import { CreateAccount } from './create_account.js';
import { FetchAndDeleteFiles } from './delete_file.js';

function App()
{
	return (
		<Router>
			<Routes>
				<Route path='/' element={ <Homepage /> }/>
				<Route path='/actions' element={ <Actions /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/custom_page' element={ <CustomPage /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/uploader' element={ <Uploader /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/choose_theme' element={ <ChooseTheme /> }/>
				<Route path='/success' element={ <Success /> }/>
				<Route path='/fail' element={ <Fail /> }/>
				<Route path='/login' element={ <Login />}/>
				<Route path='/createaccount' element= {<CreateAccount />} />
				<Route path='/action/delete_file' element= {<FetchAndDeleteFiles />} />
				<Route path='*' element={ <Error404 /> }/>
			</Routes>
		</Router>
	);
}

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'));
root.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <App />
  </React.StrictMode>
);

HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Length: 2132
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

server
{
    server_name perlouze_du_web
    domain localhost
    listen 8081
    size_limit 100
    root ./website/build/
    error_page 404 index.html
    redirect default /actions
    redirect form /success /fail

    method GET POST DELETE
    location /
    {
       method GET
       root ./website/build/
       index index.html
    }
    location /actions/
    {
       method GET
       alias index.html
       index index.html
    }
    location /static/js/
    {
       method GET
       root ./website/build/static/js/
    }
    location /static/css/
    {
       method GET
       root ./website/build/static/css/
    }
    location /static/media/
    {
       method GET
       root ./website/build/static/media/
    }
    location /src/
    {
       method GET
       root ./website/src/
    }
    location /upload
    {
       method POST GET
       root ./upload/
       redirect 302 form
    }
    location /download
    {
        method GET
        auto_index on
        root ./download/
    }
    location /delete
    {
       method GET DELETE
       root ./delete/
       auto_index on
    }
    location /createcustom
    {
       method GET POST
       root ./custom/custom_data
       cgi ./website/websiteCGI/custom_page.py
    }
    location /themedark
    {
       method POST
       Set-Cookie "theme=dark"
       redirect 302 default
    }
    location /themelight
    {
       method POST
       Set-Cookie "theme=light"
       redirect 302 default
    }
    location /success
    {
       method GET
    }
    location /fail
    {
        method GET
    }
    location /login
    {
        method GET
    }
    location /createAccount
    {
        method GET
    }
    location /connect
    {
        method POST
        cgi ./website/src/database/connect.py
    }
    location /signup
    {
        method POST GET
        cgi ./website/src/database/signup.py
    }
    location /logout
    {
        method POST
        Unset-Cookie "session_id"
        redirect 302 default
    }
    location /database
    {
        method GET
        database ./website/src/database.json strongpassword
    }
}

import React from 'react';
import './assets/styles/global.css';
import { Actions } from './actions.js';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client';
import { Homepage }  from './homepage.js';
import { Error404 } from './404.js';
import { CustomPage } from './customPage.js';
import { Uploader } from './uploader.js'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom';
import { ChooseTheme } from './choose_theme.js';
import { Success } from './success.js';
import { Fail } from './fail.js'
import { Login } from './login.js'
import { CreateAccount } from './create_account.js';
import { FetchAndDeleteFiles } from './delete_file.js';

function App()
{
	return (
		<Router>
			<Routes>
				<Route path='/' element={ <Homepage /> }/>
				<Route path='/actions' element={ <Actions /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/custom_page' element={ <CustomPage /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/uploader' element={ <Uploader /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/choose_theme' element={ <ChooseTheme /> }/>
				<Route path='/success' element={ <Success /> }/>
				<Route path='/fail' element={ <Fail /> }/>
				<Route path='/login' element={ <Login />}/>
				<Route path='/createaccount' element= {<CreateAccount />} />
				<Route path='/action/delete_file' element= {<FetchAndDeleteFiles />} />
				<Route path='*' element={ <Error404 /> }/>
			</Routes>
		</Router>
	);
}

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'));
root.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <App />
  </React.StrictMode>
);

import React from 'react';
import './assets/styles/global.css';
import { Actions } from './actions.js';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client';
import { Homepage }  from './homepage.js';
import { Error404 } from './404.js';
import { CustomPage } from './customPage.js';
import { Uploader } from './uploader.js'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom';
import { ChooseTheme } from './choose_theme.js';
import { Success } from './success.js';
import { Fail } from './fail.js'
import { Login } from './login.js'
import { CreateAccount } from './create_account.js';
import { FetchAndDeleteFiles } from './delete_file.js';

function App()
{
	return (
		<Router>
			<Routes>
				<Route path='/' element={ <Homepage /> }/>
				<Route path='/actions' element={ <Actions /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/custom_page' element={ <CustomPage /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/uploader' element={ <Uploader /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/choose_theme' element={ <ChooseTheme /> }/>
				<Route path='/success' element={ <Success /> }/>
				<Route path='/fail' element={ <Fail /> }/>
				<Route path='/login' element={ <Login />}/>
				<Route path='/createaccount' element= {<CreateAccount />} />
				<Route path='/action/delete_file' element= {<FetchAndDeleteFiles />} />
				<Route path='*' element={ <Error404 /> }/>
			</Routes>
		</Router>
	);
}

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'));
root.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <App />
  </React.StrictMode>
);

import React from 'react';
import './assets/styles/global.css';
import { Actions } from './actions.js';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client';
import { Homepage }  from './homepage.js';
import { Error404 } from './404.js';
import { CustomPage } from './customPage.js';
import { Uploader } from './uploader.js'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom';
import { ChooseTheme } from './choose_theme.js';
import { Success } from './success.js';
import { Fail } from './fail.js'
import { Login } from './login.js'
import { CreateAccount } from './create_account.js';
import { FetchAndDeleteFiles } from './delete_file.js';

function App()
{
	return (
		<Router>
			<Routes>
				<Route path='/' element={ <Homepage /> }/>
				<Route path='/actions' element={ <Actions /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/custom_page' element={ <CustomPage /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/uploader' element={ <Uploader /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/choose_theme' element={ <ChooseTheme /> }/>
				<Route path='/success' element={ <Success /> }/>
				<Route path='/fail' element={ <Fail /> }/>
				<Route path='/login' element={ <Login />}/>
				<Route path='/createaccount' element= {<CreateAccount />} />
				<Route path='/action/delete_file' element= {<FetchAndDeleteFiles />} />
				<Route path='*' element={ <Error404 /> }/>
			</Routes>
		</Router>
	);
}

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'));
root.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <App />
  </React.StrictMode>
);

import React from 'react';
import './assets/styles/global.css';
import { Actions } from './actions.js';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client';
import { Homepage }  from './homepage.js';
import { Error404 } from './404.js';
import { CustomPage } from './customPage.js';
import { Uploader } from './uploader.js'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom';
import { ChooseTheme } from './choose_theme.js';
import { Success } from './success.js';
import { Fail } from './fail.js'
import { Login } from './login.js'
import { CreateAccount } from './create_account.js';
import { FetchAndDeleteFiles } from './delete_file.js';

function App()
{
	return (
		<Router>
			<Routes>
				<Route path='/' element={ <Homepage /> }/>
				<Route path='/actions' element={ <Actions /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/custom_page' element={ <CustomPage /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/uploader' element={ <Uploader /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/choose_theme' element={ <ChooseTheme /> }/>
				<Route path='/success' element={ <Success /> }/>
				<Route path='/fail' element={ <Fail /> }/>
				<Route path='/login' element={ <Login />}/>
				<Route path='/createaccount' element= {<CreateAccount />} />
				<Route path='/action/delete_file' element= {<FetchAndDeleteFiles />} />
				<Route path='*' element={ <Error404 /> }/>
			</Routes>
		</Router>
	);
}

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'));
root.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <App />
  </React.StrictMode>
);

import React from 'react';
import './assets/styles/global.css';
import { Actions } from './actions.js';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client';
import { Homepage }  from './homepage.js';
import { Error404 } from './404.js';
import { CustomPage } from './customPage.js';
import { Uploader } from './uploader.js'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom';
import { ChooseTheme } from './choose_theme.js';
import { Success } from './success.js';
import { Fail } from './fail.js'
import { Login } from './login.js'
import { CreateAccount } from './create_account.js';
import { FetchAndDeleteFiles } from './delete_file.js';

function App()
{
	return (
		<Router>
			<Routes>
				<Route path='/' element={ <Homepage /> }/>
				<Route path='/actions' element={ <Actions /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/custom_page' element={ <CustomPage /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/uploader' element={ <Uploader /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/choose_theme' element={ <ChooseTheme /> }/>
				<Route path='/success' element={ <Success /> }/>
				<Route path='/fail' element={ <Fail /> }/>
				<Route path='/login' element={ <Login />}/>
				<Route path='/createaccount' element= {<CreateAccount />} />
				<Route path='/action/delete_file' element= {<FetchAndDeleteFiles />} />
				<Route path='*' element={ <Error404 /> }/>
			</Routes>
		</Router>
	);
}

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'));
root.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <App />
  </React.StrictMode>
);

import React from 'react';
import './assets/styles/global.css';
import { Actions } from './actions.js';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client';
import { Homepage }  from './homepage.js';
import { Error404 } from './404.js';
import { CustomPage } from './customPage.js';
import { Uploader } from './uploader.js'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom';
import { ChooseTheme } from './choose_theme.js';
import { Success } from './success.js';
import { Fail } from './fail.js'
import { Login } from './login.js'
import { CreateAccount } from './create_account.js';
import { FetchAndDeleteFiles } from './delete_file.js';

function App()
{
	return (
		<Router>
			<Routes>
				<Route path='/' element={ <Homepage /> }/>
				<Route path='/actions' element={ <Actions /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/custom_page' element={ <CustomPage /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/uploader' element={ <Uploader /> }/>
				<Route path='/action/choose_theme' element={ <ChooseTheme /> }/>
				<Route path='/success' element={ <Success /> }/>
				<Route path='/fail' element={ <Fail /> }/>
				<Route path='/login' element={ <Login />}/>
				<Route path='/createaccount' element= {<CreateAccount />} />
				<Route path='/action/delete_file' element= {<FetchAndDeleteFiles />} />
				<Route path='*' element={ <Error404 /> }/>
			</Routes>
		</Router>
	);
}

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'));
root.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <App />
  </React.StrictMode>
);
